data.event: Many believe the origin of the Prospect community began when Preston Locklear claimed large swaths of land along what is known today as the Long Swamp.

data.event: It was established by the Scottish around 1875.
Preston's original sanctuary was built in 1948.
The present sanctuary was built in the late 1970's with the addition of a fellowship hall and small apartment for visiting preachers in the 1990's.
